                     Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols. 104va-106vb)&#xD; - Lǝfāfa ṣǝdq “Bandlet of
                     Righteousness” (fols. 111ra-114rb)&#xD; - Mangada samāy “Journey to Heaven”
                     (fols. 114rb-115ra).</summary>
